name: VaderAI by Virtuals
description: VaderAI by Virtuals is a blockchain project designed to establish a significant presence in the emerging Agentic Economy, which is a novel economic framework characterized by the use of autonomous agents for financial operations. The platform is structured around a Decentralized Autonomous Organization (DAO) framework, which includes both passive and active DAOs. This structure allows for the autonomous management and trading of Agent tokens, thereby optimizing asset management processes within this new economic model.
